en-US.title: Santa Paula West Medical Group and Pediatrics
en-US.description: Located in Santa Paula, California, Santa Paula West Medical Group and Pediatrics has been recognized for its outstanding health services provided to the LGBTQ+ community, including those who identify as transgender, non-binary, or queer, with a special focus on trans-affirming care. They are known for their empathetic and respectful treatment of all patients, making it a safe and welcoming environment for all.

address: 254 W Harvard Blvd B, Santa Paula, CA 93060, USA
